    <desc lang="en">A prominent AI expert has issued a stark warning that a wave of unemployment will occur in 2026 due to AI systems, with nearly 100 million jobs worldwide potentially being replaced. In this rapidly evolving society, children's futures are fraught with uncertainty. "What career do you dream of when you grow up?" Even with hard work towards their goals, children may still be overtaken by AI as adults. How can parents plan for their children's future? The program uses AI to illustrate the future evolution of related professions, designing "growth programs" for three celebrity actors and their children. This allows parents to closely observe whether their chosen lifestyle is suitable for their children and themselves, while also considering the future possibilities of their own careers.</desc>
